claim.claim-text:
A method for manufacturing a vacuum insulation material, comprising:
preparing a core material;
compressing and packing an overall surface of the core material with an inner bag made of an air-permeable film;
placing a getter on the inner bag; and
vacuum-packing the inner bag with a cover material.

A method for manufacturing a vacuum insulation material, comprising:
preparing a core material;
inserting a getter into the core material;
compressing and packing an overall surface of the core material including the getter with an inner bag made of an air-permeable film; and
vacuum-packing the inner bag with a cover material.
